{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "舞台上的怪物人偶第4话 再续未完的故事",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "演出取消，但莱姬希却没有放弃。\\n她决定自己写完剧本。\\n“要抛弃那眼看就要完成的心吗？”，\\n加斯特因莱姬希的质问深受触动，于是\\n为了拯救梅洛的妹妹而开始制作新的熏香。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "万圣节也彻底结束了呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "演出……也被其它剧目所代替。\\n我们的准备也都白费了呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "也没能看到“心”完成的瞬间……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——予以否定。还不能放弃。\\n——诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——还有我们能做的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "诶？你说你还是想演出？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "予以肯定。舞台布景和表演练习\\n基本都完成了。只要完成剧本的结局，\\n就能进行演出。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "嗯……\\n因为调整了演出日程的原因，\\n倒是确实空出了几个档期。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "可是……梅洛现在还在\\n家里闷着吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "这样的话，他真的还会\\n再继续写这次的脚本吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "这方面没有问题，\\n因为剧本……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "唉……\\n还是……不行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "加斯特，你怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是莱姬希啊。\\n嗯，最近我不管怎样都没法专心研究。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "哈哈……看来梅洛兄妹的事\\n对我影响不小啊。\\n虽说我不至于像当事人那样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——毕竟你在梅洛身上\\n看到了自己的影子呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是啊，所以我非常能理解当自己的\\n努力化为泡影时有多失望。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "而且我也曾给雪莉\\n送去过治愈熏香。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "明明我也治好过那种病的。\\n但是……我的熏香这次\\n却没能起到任何作用。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "明明说了要救她，\\n结果却是如此……\\n我觉得自己很没用。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "加斯特……\\n你不要过于自责。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "嗯……我知道。\\n我没有时间沮丧。毕竟演出\\n取消后还要收拾烂摊子呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——予以否定。你不用收拾。\\n但是……我希望你能登台。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "登台？什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我和剧场老板商量过了。\\n只要能完成剧本，戏就可以上演。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "所以……\\n就由我来完成剧本。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "什么！？你要写剧本？\\n可是……你会写吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "并无经验，所以成功概率不明。\\n但即便如此，我也要写。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "真是乱来……虽说剧本只差结尾……\\n但结尾也正是最关键，\\n也是最难的部分啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "因为难……\\n就要放弃吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "因为难就不做了吗？\\n因为难就不去完成了，这样好吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "本应通过这个剧本……这场演出\\n而诞生的“心”，还未能诞生。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "然而却被如此轻易地抛弃。\\n仅仅是因为……它没有生命吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "无论是你，还是梅洛，\\n你们制作的熏香和剧本都是\\n为了拯救自己珍视之人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "那么这场演出……\\n就不值得你们珍视吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "这……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——莱姬希，不要为难加斯特啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "不过……加斯特，莱姬希一直\\n期待着演出完成的那一刻。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "说是如果梅洛完成了这次演出，\\n也许就能明白麦斯特罗把我们\\n造出来时是什么心情了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "所以，她对梅洛这次放弃了\\n演出感到很“悲伤”。\\n还请你能够理解。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "悲伤……\\n原来如此……\\n你们也是被创造出的一方……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "看到作品被抛弃的那一刻……\\n应该很难受吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——我怎样都无所谓……\\n但这场演出一定在等待着\\n自己被完成的那一刻。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我能明白它的心情。\\n因为我的心，正是麦斯特罗\\n所完成的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "所以，我会按照从梅洛那里\\n听来的故事，把剧本写到最后。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "而且……如果创造一种东西\\n能够拯救一个人的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我所完成的东西，也许也能够\\n产生拯救他人的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "那个人有可能是沮丧的你，\\n也有可能是绝望的梅洛，\\n亦或是徘徊在生死边缘的雪莉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "嗯……\\n谢谢你，莱姬希。我醒悟过来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "为了拯救他人的心……\\n我也应该停止自责，\\n然后去做力所能及的事啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——加斯特？\\n你要去哪？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我要去森隐族的森林，\\n去采集一些药草。\\n我要把一切可能有效的药草都找来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "你是……要为病危的雪莉\\n制作新的熏香吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "嗯，若是我做的东西能够拯救\\n他人的话……我自然也不能止步不前。\\n对吧，莱姬希？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——加斯特……\\n好的，我会一边写剧本，\\n一边等你回来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "嗯，就这么定了。\\n我一定会治好雪莉，\\n拯救梅洛的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "拯救所有人对这场\\n演出付出的心！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}